    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Roles] AS [r]) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
2024-02-21 23:05:42.644 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (164ms) [Parameters=[@p0='?' (Size = 4000), @p1='?' (Size = 4000), @p2='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SET IMPLICIT_TRANSACTIONS OFF;
SET NOCOUNT ON;
MERGE [Roles] USING (
VALUES (@p0, 0),
(@p1, 1),
(@p2, 2)) AS i ([RoleName], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([RoleName])
VALUES (i.[RoleName])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[RoleId], i._Position;

    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Users] AS [u]
        WHERE [u].[Username] = N'superuser') THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
